&quot;Vox died today on E'ci and she dropped the Hide. Also Dropped 2 tomes and a eyepatch. So yes it is Vox that drops the hide.&quot; Ladayen<BR>
<BR>
I don't think that Verant changed the Bard quest at all. Bards still need the White Dragon Scale for their epic quest. They only lessened the competition for the same item which is also an extremely rare drop against other classes. Bards also need the Red Dragon Scale which is not only used for the Bard Epic, but also for the Warrior Epic and the Red Dragonscale Armor Quest (wearable by 6 different classes).<BR>
<BR>
And yet again, another succesful Vox raid is posted without a single white scale drop. The hide will probably drop more often than the ever elusive WDS.<BR>

