There is a quest that originates in RM for a cloak which also required the ever ellusive white scale. This quest has been changed, not the Bard epic. This eliminates the competion between classes for the white scale which has only 3 known sources, Voxx, Gore, and Nortlaf the scale Keeper. (Note: I can find no one that has ever seen Nortlaf drop a white scale all though it is said he does.)<BR>
